reviewText: I like it this movie, but it is have different format and it is not possible play on american CD recorder, pc, television, dvd..You must buy special device :/

When I was growing up I couldn't get enough of my favorite Czech fairytales. This is one of the best ones. My favorite part is when the prince (who is undercover as a gardener) sings the song in the garden and captures the princesses attention. At first the princess is snobby and rude, but when she realizes it gets her nowhere she opens up and asks to learn the song with the 'gardener'.
